title: Red Bull BC One 2005 - World Breakdancing Championship
description:
Red Bull BC One takes you inside one of the most prestigious breakdancing events in the world, as top breakers battle it out in the fiercest dance competition ever seen. Special performances by a collection of B-boy legends and champions, including hip hop icon Storm and pop and lock duo Hilto and Bosch. Hosted by the Godfather of Noyze, Rahzel (The Roots) also gives a special performance of the sickest beatboxing ever heard. Hosted In Berlin.

Featuring 16 of the best B-Boys in the world: Physicx (Korea), Lilou (France), Omar (USA), Bennie (South Africa), Jora (Russia), Junior (France), Born (Korea), Ronnie (USA), Moy (USA), Hong 10 (Korea), Brahim (France), Machine (USA), Cico (Italy), Pelezinho (Brazil), Rubber Legz (Germany), and Sonic (Denmark)
